<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM9.10">
<l>tēṉakumā malarkkūntaṟ kaucalaiyuñ cumittiraiyuñ cintai nōvak</l>
<l>kūṉuruvil koṭuntoḻuttai coṟkēṭṭa koṭiyavaḷtaṉ coṟkoṇ ṭiṉṟu</l>
<l>kāṉakamē mikavirumpi nītuṟanta vaḷanakarait tuṟantu nāṉum</l>
<l>vāṉakamē mikavirumpip pōkiṉṟēṉ maṉukulattār taṅkaḷ kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am going to heaven, greatly desiring [it], also renouncing the wealthy city,</l>
<l>which You renounced today greatly desiring the forest,</l>
<l>accepting the words of the cruel woman</l>
<l rend="indent">who listened to the words of the maidservant as crooked as [her] hunchbacked form,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that Sumitrā and Kausalyā</l>
<l rend="indent">—with long tresses with big, blooming flowers [brimming] with honey—</l>
<l rend="indent">are aggrieved in their minds.</l>
<l>O King of the people of Manu’s lineage!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
